reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great product at a great price!
reviews.reviewText: I was hesitant about purchasing a new charging cord for my iPhone, thinking it would be too costly like other Apple accessories that I’ve purchased in the past. I was thrilled when I found this set of chargers on Amazon! They arrived within 24 hours and were packaged very nicely. They came with an attractive carrying pouch which was a real bonus. I started using them immediately and have found them to be of good quality and give a fast charge. This is really important to me, because I often forget to put my phone on the charger! I was really grateful for the super long cords which give me easy access from across the room. I’m very satisfied with the chargers and will be ordering from them again. My daughter saw mine and plans to buy a set, too. Thanks for a quality product at an affordable price!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 30, 2023
reviews.reviewText: So glad I found this charging cord; its fast at charging and seems to be flexible & durable. Fits my iPhone SE2 perfect and no issues with my OtterBox case. I love having the extra length so I don't have to hanging over the edge of the chair. To my surprise they came with a small drawstring bag which is perfect to carry in my purse without getting tangled up in things. I definitely would recommend this product!
